{"id":"ZPRAC_CDS_DCL","title":"level access based on user authorization","phase":10,"phaseName":"Analytics & Security","category":"Analytics & Security","subcategory":"Authorization","language":"abap","description":"Restrict row-level access based on user authorization. Key topics: DCL is a SEPARATE artifact from the CDS view — file extension .asr. The CDS view must have @AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK. DCL uses ASPECT = PVZM to define mapping between fields and auth objects.","sections":[{"title":"Key Learning Points","description":"<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>DCL is a SEPARATE artifact from the CDS view — file extension .asr</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>The CDS view must have @AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>DCL uses ASPECT = PVZM to define mapping between fields and auth objects</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Implicit access control is based on PFCG authorization object fields</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>DCL can restrict: SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE (per operation)</span></div></div>"},{"title":"Concept Diagram","description":"<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-g\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#22C55E\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-r\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#EF4444\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">DCL — Access Control Flow</text>\n\n  <!-- === FLOW DIAGRAM === -->\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">1. User Request</text>\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"90\" width=\"130\" height=\"45\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"105\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#16A34A\">SAP User / OData</text>\n  <text x=\"105\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">via Fiori or API</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"170\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"290\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">2. CDS View Accessed</text>\n  <rect x=\"215\" y=\"90\" width=\"160\" height=\"45\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"295\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">CDS View Entity</text>\n  <text x=\"295\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"375\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"415\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">3. DCL Security Check</text>\n  <rect x=\"420\" y=\"90\" width=\"170\" height=\"45\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"505\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#DC2626\">DCL: define role</text>\n  <text x=\"505\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">PFCG → aspect mapping</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"590\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"630\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Decision diamond -->\n  <polygon points=\"715,67 800,112 715,157 630,112\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"715\" y=\"108\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Access</text>\n  <text x=\"715\" y=\"122\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Granted?</text>\n\n  <!-- GRANTED -->\n  <line x1=\"800\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"870\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr-g)\"/>\n  <rect x=\"875\" y=\"92\" width=\"110\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"930\" y=\"112\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Data Returned</text>\n  <text x=\"930\" y=\"126\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">Row-filtered set</text>\n\n  <!-- DENIED -->\n  <line x1=\"630\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"630\" y2=\"200\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr-r)\"/>\n  <rect x=\"565\" y=\"205\" width=\"130\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"630\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">No Data / Suppressed</text>\n\n  <!-- === DCL SYNTAX === -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"270\" width=\"450\" height=\"190\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"295\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#22C55E\">DCL: define role Syntax</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"318\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@MappingRole: true</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"335\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@MappingRoleName: 'ZPRAC_TRAVEL_SALES'</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"352\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">define role ZPRAC_TRAVEL_SALES {</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"369\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#EAB308\">  grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</text>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"386\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  where (AgencyId) =</text>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"403\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    aspect pfcg_auth(</text>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"420\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  org_value, 'S_CARRID', 'ACTVT'</text>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"437\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  );</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"454\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">}</text>\n\n  <!-- DCL explanation -->\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"270\" width=\"450\" height=\"190\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"295\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">How DCL Works</text>\n  <line x1=\"530\" y1=\"302\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"302\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"322\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">1.</tspan> User accesses a CDS view via OData / SE16</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"342\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">2.</tspan> CDS annotation <tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"362\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">3.</tspan> DCL role is evaluated at runtime</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"382\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">4.</tspan> PFCG authorization object is checked</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"402\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">5.</tspan> If match → row is visible; otherwise → hidden</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"427\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">S_CARRID = Authorization object for airline</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"445\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">ACTVT = Activity (03=display, 02=change, 01=create)</text>\n\n  <!-- === ACCESS CONTROL MODES === -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"480\" width=\"920\" height=\"140\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FFF3ED\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck — 3 Modes</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"512\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"512\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"60\" y=\"525\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">#CHECK</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"565\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Default. DCL role is checked.</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"583\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">If no DCL exists → no data returned.</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"598\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Use for most production views.</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"360\" y=\"525\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">#NOT_REQUIRED</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"565\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">DCL role is NOT checked.</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"583\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">All users see all rows.</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"598\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Use for tech / utility views only.</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"660\" y=\"525\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">#PRIVILEGED_ONLY</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"565\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Only DCL-defined users pass.</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"583\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Restrictive — no default access.</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"598\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Use for sensitive / financial data.</text>\n\n  <!-- PFCG mapping -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"635\" width=\"920\" height=\"95\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"658\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">PFCG Authorization → DCL Mapping Pipeline</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"665\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"665\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"60\" y=\"678\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#FFF\">PFCG Role</text>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"711\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">SAP Role assignment</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"698\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"698\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"265\" y=\"678\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"345\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#FFF\">Auth Object</text>\n  <text x=\"345\" y=\"711\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">S_CARRID, ACTVT</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"425\" y1=\"698\" x2=\"465\" y2=\"698\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"470\" y=\"678\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#FFF\">DCL: aspect</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"711\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">pfcg_auth() mapping</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"630\" y1=\"698\" x2=\"670\" y2=\"698\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"675\" y=\"678\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"755\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#FFF\">CDS Row Filter</text>\n  <text x=\"755\" y=\"711\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">WHERE clause injected</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"835\" y1=\"698\" x2=\"875\" y2=\"698\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"880\" y=\"678\" width=\"70\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"915\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Data</text>\n<text x=\"10\" y=\"20\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(233,84,32,0.15)\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">cds-bytes (c) 2026</text></svg></div>"}],"content":"<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_DCL-key-learning-points\">Key Learning Points</h2>\n<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>DCL is a SEPARATE artifact from the CDS view — file extension .asr</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>The CDS view must have @AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>DCL uses ASPECT = PVZM to define mapping between fields and auth objects</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Implicit access control is based on PFCG authorization object fields</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>DCL can restrict: SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE (per operation)</span></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_DCL-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-g\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#22C55E\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-r\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#EF4444\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">DCL — Access Control Flow</text>\n\n  <!-- === FLOW DIAGRAM === -->\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">1. User Request</text>\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"90\" width=\"130\" height=\"45\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"105\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#16A34A\">SAP User / OData</text>\n  <text x=\"105\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">via Fiori or API</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"170\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"290\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">2. CDS View Accessed</text>\n  <rect x=\"215\" y=\"90\" width=\"160\" height=\"45\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"295\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">CDS View Entity</text>\n  <text x=\"295\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"375\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"415\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">3. DCL Security Check</text>\n  <rect x=\"420\" y=\"90\" width=\"170\" height=\"45\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"505\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#DC2626\">DCL: define role</text>\n  <text x=\"505\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">PFCG → aspect mapping</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"590\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"630\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Decision diamond -->\n  <polygon points=\"715,67 800,112 715,157 630,112\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"715\" y=\"108\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Access</text>\n  <text x=\"715\" y=\"122\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Granted?</text>\n\n  <!-- GRANTED -->\n  <line x1=\"800\" y1=\"112\" x2=\"870\" y2=\"112\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr-g)\"/>\n  <rect x=\"875\" y=\"92\" width=\"110\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"930\" y=\"112\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Data Returned</text>\n  <text x=\"930\" y=\"126\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">Row-filtered set</text>\n\n  <!-- DENIED -->\n  <line x1=\"630\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"630\" y2=\"200\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr-r)\"/>\n  <rect x=\"565\" y=\"205\" width=\"130\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"630\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">No Data / Suppressed</text>\n\n  <!-- === DCL SYNTAX === -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"270\" width=\"450\" height=\"190\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"295\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#22C55E\">DCL: define role Syntax</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"318\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@MappingRole: true</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"335\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">@MappingRoleName: 'ZPRAC_TRAVEL_SALES'</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"352\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">define role ZPRAC_TRAVEL_SALES {</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"369\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#EAB308\">  grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</text>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"386\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  where (AgencyId) =</text>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"403\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">    aspect pfcg_auth(</text>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"420\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  org_value, 'S_CARRID', 'ACTVT'</text>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"437\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  );</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"454\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">}</text>\n\n  <!-- DCL explanation -->\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"270\" width=\"450\" height=\"190\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"295\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">How DCL Works</text>\n  <line x1=\"530\" y1=\"302\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"302\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"322\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">1.</tspan> User accesses a CDS view via OData / SE16</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"342\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">2.</tspan> CDS annotation <tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK</tspan></text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"362\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">3.</tspan> DCL role is evaluated at runtime</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"382\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">4.</tspan> PFCG authorization object is checked</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"402\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">5.</tspan> If match → row is visible; otherwise → hidden</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"427\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">S_CARRID = Authorization object for airline</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"445\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">ACTVT = Activity (03=display, 02=change, 01=create)</text>\n\n  <!-- === ACCESS CONTROL MODES === -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"480\" width=\"920\" height=\"140\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FFF3ED\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck — 3 Modes</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"512\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"512\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"60\" y=\"525\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">#CHECK</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"565\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Default. DCL role is checked.</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"583\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">If no DCL exists → no data returned.</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"598\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Use for most production views.</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"360\" y=\"525\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">#NOT_REQUIRED</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"565\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">DCL role is NOT checked.</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"583\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">All users see all rows.</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"598\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Use for tech / utility views only.</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"660\" y=\"525\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">#PRIVILEGED_ONLY</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"565\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Only DCL-defined users pass.</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"583\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Restrictive — no default access.</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"598\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Use for sensitive / financial data.</text>\n\n  <!-- PFCG mapping -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"635\" width=\"920\" height=\"95\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"658\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">PFCG Authorization → DCL Mapping Pipeline</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"665\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"665\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"60\" y=\"678\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#FFF\">PFCG Role</text>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"711\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">SAP Role assignment</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"698\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"698\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"265\" y=\"678\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"345\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#FFF\">Auth Object</text>\n  <text x=\"345\" y=\"711\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">S_CARRID, ACTVT</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"425\" y1=\"698\" x2=\"465\" y2=\"698\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"470\" y=\"678\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#FFF\">DCL: aspect</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"711\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">pfcg_auth() mapping</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"630\" y1=\"698\" x2=\"670\" y2=\"698\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"675\" y=\"678\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"755\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#FFF\">CDS Row Filter</text>\n  <text x=\"755\" y=\"711\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">WHERE clause injected</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"835\" y1=\"698\" x2=\"875\" y2=\"698\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"880\" y=\"678\" width=\"70\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"915\" y=\"698\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Data</text>\n<text x=\"10\" y=\"20\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(233,84,32,0.15)\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">cds-bytes (c) 2026</text></svg></div>","tags":["cds-views"],"details":"<p class=\"mb-2\">WHAT IS DCL?</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DCL (Data Control Language) is a CDS artifact (.asr file) that</p><p class=\"mb-2\">defines row-level security for CDS views. It works with PFCG</p><p class=\"mb-2\">authorization objects to filter data per user.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DCL SYNTAX OVERVIEW:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@EndUserText.label: 'Access control for ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE'</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@MappingRole: true</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">COMMON DCL PATTERNS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">┌──────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┐</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Pattern                          │ When to use                    │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">├──────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────┤</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ grant select ... where ...       │ Standard row-level restriction │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ grant all on ...                 │ Full access (admin purpose)    │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ inherit access for ...           │ Delegate to underlying view    │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ aspect pfcg_auth(...)            │ Map CDS field to PFCG auth obj │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ $sy_user_agr()                   │ User's authorization values    │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">└──────────────────────────────────┴────────────────────────────────┘</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — INHERIT ACCESS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Delegate access control to an underlying view. The current view</p><p class=\"mb-2\">inherits the DCL restrictions from its data source automatically.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@EndUserText.label: 'DCL for ZPRAC_CDS_VIEW_ON_VIEW (inherits)'</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@MappingRole: true</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_VON_V_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_VIEW_ON_VIEW {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant inherited access for select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE;</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — DEFINE ASPECT:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Create reusable authorization conditions for multiple roles.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@EndUserText.label: 'Aspect for Agency authorization'</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define aspect ZPRAC_ASPECT_AGENCY {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() )</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect ZPRAC_ASPECT_AGENCY;</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — CONDITIONAL GRANTS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Grant different access levels based on user authorization values.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_TRAVEL_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant insert, update, delete on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '01,02', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — INSTANCE-BASED ACCESS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Restrict access to specific instances based on field values.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Multiple WHERE conditions can be combined with AND/OR.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() )</p><p class=\"mb-2\">and (Status) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV_STATUS, ACTVT = '03', STATUS = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — ACCESS POLICIES FOR READ/WRITE:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Use different PFCG activities for read vs write access.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant insert on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '01', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant update on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '02', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">BEST PRACTICE RULES:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">┌────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┐</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Rule                                           │ Reason                     │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">├────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────┤</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Always use @AccessControl.authorizationCheck   │ Required for DCL to apply  │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Use #CHECK at consumption layer                │ Enforces row-level security│</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Use inherit access for VDM layer stacking      │ Avoids DCL duplication     │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Use define aspect for reusable conditions      │ DRY principle              │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Grant different activities per operation       │ Principle of least privilege│</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Never use DCL on private/interface views       │ Internal views don't need it│</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Always run unit tests with DISABLE_DCL         │ Avoid flaky tests          │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">└────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────────────────────────┘</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DIAGRAM: assets/diagrams/dcl-flow.svg</p>","cdsViewName":"","sqlViewName":"","topic":"Data Control Language — @AccessControl.authorizationCheck"}